branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series TU tubing represents a new high quality standard in metric size polyurethane tubing.  Series TUH, hard polyurethane tubing, is available in a standard or high pressure type and TUS is a soft polyurethane tubing.  
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
The TCU series is a polyurethane coil tubing that is very flexible and makes compact piping possible.  The TCU series comes in three different tube sizes and comes in the standard color of black.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
The TFU series is a flat polyurethane tubing, which makes compact piping possible.  TFU is available in three different tube models as  standard and up to 3 tubes available for each model.  Standard color is black.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Series TAU is designed for air pressure piping to product or assembly while preventing static electricity.  It is made of a conductive polyurethane  material and is available in black 20m or 100m rolls.
&lt;/p&gt;
